## Section 3 — Untrusted Source Flag: GCS Bucket `p-2-cen1`

The `artemislivetracker.com` site fetches from an anonymous Google Cloud Storage bucket at `storage.googleapis.com/…/p-2-cen1/`. This is **not a NASA domain**. The path prefix `October/1/October` does not correspond to Artemis II’s April 2026 timeline — suggesting stale test data or Artemis I content. There is no verifiable provenance. **Exclude entirely from our tracker.**

